---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.14-1, voms-admin-client v. 2.0.7-1, voms-admin-interface v. 2.0.2-1

   Updated voms-admin interface documentation.
   
   Deprecated old ACL interface methods.
   
   Added VOMS-Admin User's guide
   
   Improved voms-admin client online documentation
   
   Fixes for the following bugs:
   
   https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?34612
   https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?34201
   https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?34200
   https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?34112
   
   
   
---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.13-1
   
   Real fix for https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?31791 : the 2.0.12 fix introduced
   a deployment problem on mysql installations.
   
   The disable-webui-requests option is now again supported in the voms-admin-configure
   script.

---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.12-1
   
   Fixes for the following bugs:
   
   https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?32527 (tentative, since I wasn't able to reproduce it)
   https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?31791
   

---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.11-1
   
   Fix for bug http://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?33029
   
   
---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.10-1, voms-admin-client v. 2.0.6-1, voms-admin-interface v. 2.0.1-1

   Refactored voms-admin-ping script included in the voms-admin-server rpm.
   
   Added ACL support to command-line client.
   Added ACL management web service (compatible with client >= 2.0.6-1)
   
   Added Registration web service.
   
   Fixes for the following bugs:
   
     https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?12168
     https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?30726
     https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?32147
     https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?32148
     https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?31790
     https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?31787
     https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?31667

---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.9-1

   Fix for bug https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?31068.
   
   Fix for bug https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?30728.

   Introduction of the configuration page.
   
   Introduction of a flag that allows to generate grid-mapfile with
   DNs email component encoded also in the /emailAddress= format
   (in addition to the the /Email= format).This configuration flag 
   is contained in the voms.service.properties configuration file 
   and is turned off by default.

---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.8-1, voms-admin-client v. 2.0.5-1
   
   voms-admin client list-group typo fix, https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?29566 .
   Fixed packaging of the "full" voms admin rpm (containing server, client and
   interface files).


---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.7-1, voms-admin-client v.2.0.4-1
   
   Fixed packaging as requested after the dependency challenge.
   
   Now four rpms are produced for each voms-admin build:
   * the full voms-admin rpm (containing server, client and interface)
   * the server rpm
   * the client rpm
   * the interface rpm
   
   Other rpm packaging issues have been fixed in this release.
   
   
---+ voms-admin-server v.2.0.6-1, voms-admin-client v.2.0.3-1
   
   Fixes for the following savannah bugs:

   * https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?29567
   * https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?29566
   * https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?29440
   * https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/?29439
   
   Removed ZSI library from the cvs source (dependency challenge refactoring).





